commentary: I Sharma to Roach, 1 run oh yes, Ishant digs it in, Roach moves back and across and fends awkwardly, he then sets off for the single. Ishant fields the ball on his follow through and then turns to throw the stumps down at the bowler's end. Roach is a few inches short but I didn't hear any strong appeals. Umpire Malcolm doesn't refer it as a result. Surely someone appealed? Harbhajan Singh signals frantically from the dressing room saying it's out but it's too late ..the game moves on ...
